    "description": "вҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ <br><br>You arrive to <strong>MARQUEZ PAZ</strong>, a remote town, far away from the capital for a jobвҖҰ What they donвҖҷt tell you, is that youвҖҷll be working for a <i>funeral home</i>вҖҰ but not just any funeral homeвҖҰ but a funeral homeвҖҰ located in <strong>MARQUEZ PAZ</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/7d540852d51b71f086b269ee3f96e603.poster.avif?t=1666983467\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/7d540852d51b71f086b269ee3f96e603.webm?t=1666983467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/7d540852d51b71f086b269ee3f96e603.mp4?t=1666983467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WE ARE A FUNERAL HOMEвҖҰ IN MARQUEZ PAZ</h2></strong></li></ul>Work for the вҖңfuneвҖқ making errands and transporting the deceasedвҖҰ <i>who knows what youвҖҷll come across along the way</i>вҖҰ<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/3f3330b30a8785bc475948e46c5b2811.poster.avif?t=1666983467\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/3f3330b30a8785bc475948e46c5b2811.webm?t=1666983467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/3f3330b30a8785bc475948e46c5b2811.mp4?t=1666983467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SUBMERGE YOURSELF IN MARQUEZ PAZ </h2></strong></li></ul>Explore and get to know itвҖҷs unique population, help them or <strong>beat the crap out of them</strong>вҖҰ (It will all depend on your moral judgement)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/34525021f02fdfdced5038df456f911e.poster.avif?t=1666983467\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/34525021f02fdfdced5038df456f911e.webm?t=1666983467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/34525021f02fdfdced5038df456f911e.mp4?t=1666983467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT TO DO IN MARQUEZ PAZ</h2></strong></li></ul>Explore the neighborhood, interact and get to know its inhabitants, enter its <strong>classic retro RPG</strong> style dungeons and fight their respective bosses, beat the living soul out of them, or maybe you just want to be running around doing errands, ignoring your responsibilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/72ffe958a149f77d0035fb9416b35efc.poster.avif?t=1666983467\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/72ffe958a149f77d0035fb9416b35efc.webm?t=1666983467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/72ffe958a149f77d0035fb9416b35efc.mp4?t=1666983467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THIS IS THE REALEST EXPERIENCE OF WHAT IT FEELS LIKE LIVING IN ARGENTINA</h2></strong></li></ul>Knowing that this <strong>вҖңopen worldвҖқ RPG/Visual Novel adventure</strong> takes place in <i>Argentina</i>, we have tons of features that reflect this experience. <br>For example, the vast and diverse cultures and accents, BBQВҙs (asados), and common problems like the unstable and changing economy and power shortages. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/d0ffcf52f8f930a466dd7b64afe50b7e.poster.avif?t=1666983467\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/d0ffcf52f8f930a466dd7b64afe50b7e.webm?t=1666983467\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885040/extras/d0ffcf52f8f930a466dd7b64afe50b7e.mp4?t=1666983467\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WISHLIST US</h2></strong><br>Wishlisting the game would really help us out a lot when it comes to our project reaching new and more people, and that would be could pretty cool tbh haha.<br><br><strong>PLEASE</strong> WISHLIST WE ARE DESPERATE<br><br>вҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ рҹ’Җвҳ ",
